original_title: Richmond: New Dorp Lane - Bay Street
text:
New Lane (left), east from Bay Street. The house is on the north side of the street near Linden Place. It belonged to the Townsend family (1874 map), and later to Mrs. Marsh (1898 map). The view is from near St. Johns P. E. Church.

April 30, 1935.

P.L. Sperr
